summary: An ordinance providing for the acquisition from King County for general municipal purposes of certain tax title property designated as unnumbered tracts in West Seattle Park and Second Plat of West Seattle by the West Seattle Land and Improvement Co; making a reimbursable appropriation from the Emergency Fund for the payment of delinquent taxes and local improvement assessments thereon and to discharge the trust; and declaring the emergency for such appropriation.
committee: Finance and Parks and Public Grounds
